iserv-sportoase (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of SportOase IServ Module
  * Modern UI design system with Tailwind CSS (compiled assets)
  * Complete booking system with capacity management
  * Admin dashboard with statistics
  * Email notification system via SMTP
  * Database migrations for PostgreSQL
  * Responsive mobile design
  * German language interface
  * Production-ready asset compilation
  * Comprehensive documentation (Setup guides for OAuth2, Email, Database)

